com.sinch.android.rtc

Interface AudioController


  • public interface AudioController
    Interface for controlling different audio settings. An AudioController object is only valid while the SinchClient is started. As soon as the SinchClient is stopped, this object is invalidated and must not be used.

    • Method Summary
